---
Name: Microsoft 365 Contact
Description: Tools for interacting with Microsoft 365 Contact.
Metadata: bundle: true
Share Tools: List Contacts, Create Contact, Update Contact, Delete Contact, Get Contact

---
Name: List Contacts
Description: List all contacts available to the user.
Tools: github.com/gptscript-ai/datasets/filter
Credential: ../../credential

#!${GPTSCRIPT_TOOL_DIR}/bin/gptscript-go-tool listContacts

---
Name: Create Contact
Description: Create a new contact in the user's Microsoft contact list.
Credential: ../../credential
Param: givenName: The given name of the contact.
Param: surname: The surname of the contact.
Param: emailAddress: The email address of the contact.
Param: businessPhone: The business phone number of the contact.

#!${GPTSCRIPT_TOOL_DIR}/bin/gptscript-go-tool createContact

--- 
Name: Update Contact
Description: Update an existing contact in the user's Microsoft contact list.
Credential: ../../credential
Param: contactID: (required) The ID of the contact to update.
Param: givenName: (optional) The given name of the contact.
Param: surname: (optional) The surname of the contact.
Param: emailAddress: (optional) The email address of the contact.
Param: businessPhone: (optional) The business phone number of the contact.

#!${GPTSCRIPT_TOOL_DIR}/bin/gptscript-go-tool updateContact

---
Name: Delete Contact
Description: Delete an existing contact from the user's Microsoft contact list.
Credential: ../../credential
Param: contactID: (required) The ID of the contact to delete.

#!${GPTSCRIPT_TOOL_DIR}/bin/gptscript-go-tool deleteContact

---
Name: Get Contact
Description: Get the details of an existing contact from the user's Microsoft contact list.
Credential: ../../credential
Param: contactID: (required) The ID of the contact to get.

#!${GPTSCRIPT_TOOL_DIR}/bin/gptscript-go-tool getContact

